{"article_id":"caqsoX3GjifdCNuG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"BREAKING :","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"State Department declares","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"22 emails on Hillary Clinton 's account ` top secret ' ;","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"wo n't release them .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"- The Associated Press","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"( @ AP )","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"January 29 , 2016","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"The intelligence community has deemed","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"some of Hillary Clinton ' s emails \" too damaging '' to national security","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to release under any circumstances ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"according to a U.S. government official close to the ongoing review .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"A second source ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"who was not authorized to speak on the record ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"backed up the finding .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"The determination was first reported by Fox News ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"hours before the State Department formally announced Friday","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that seven email chains ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"found in 22 documents ,","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"will be withheld \" in full \"","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"because they , in fact , contain \" Top Secret \" information ...","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"the Obama administration confirmed to the Associated Press","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that the seven email chains would be withheld .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"The department has since confirmed those details publicly .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"The decision","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"to withhold the documents in full ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and not provide even a partial release with redactions ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"further undercuts claims by the State Department and the Clinton campaign","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that none of the intelligence in the emails was classified","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"when it hit Clinton 's personal server .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Fox News is told","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"the emails include intelligence from `` special access programs , '' or SAP ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"which is considered beyond \" Top Secret . \"","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"State Department declares an entire Sid Blumenthal memo to be classified .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"https : //t.co/4mFiVXpAWq","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"- Byron Tau","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"( @ ByronTau )","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"January 30 , 2016","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"One WH statement contradicts the other","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"pic.twitter.com/QJqhMYXTP","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"5 - Stephen Miller","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"( @ redsteeze )","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"January 29 , 2016","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Senate Intel Committee ranking Democrat @ SenFeinstein on latest on @ HillaryClinton emails -- pic.twitter.com/XPy75PoIbu","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"- Jake Tapper","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"( @ jaketapper )","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"January 30 , 2016","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Here 's one of the classified memos","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"( this one from Sid Blumenthal )","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"which Hillary forwards .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"https : //t.co/AfOL1qOzml","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"- pic.twitter.com/RkCWWRveVC","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"- Jimmy","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"( @ JimmyPrinceton )","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"January 30 , 2016","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Shouts of `` overclassification '' are the last refuge of USG officials","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"who broke secrecy laws ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"got caught ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"and have no leg left","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"to stand on .","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"- John Schindler","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"( @ 20committee )","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"January 30 , 2016","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Hillary 's in deep trouble over # EmailGate .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"As I told you months ago .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"Hillbots are freaking out ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"as they should .","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"Some bad news ca n't be spun .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"- John Schindler","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"( @ 20committee )","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"January 30 , 2016","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Friday was a very bad day for Hillary Clinton ,","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"as her email scandal deepened in several serious ways .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Remember when her campaign angrily insisted","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"that the intelligence community 's Obama-appointed Inspector General had wrongly identified two pieces of intelligence","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"classified as 'top secret ' among the","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"( non-deleted )","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"emails on her improper unsecure private server ?","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"They tried to cast the conclusion as the product of an abstruse and benign interagency squabble with the State Department","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"-- the first of several egregious attempts","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"to question the watchdog 's motives and integrity .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Not only was the IG correct at the time ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"as Christine posted just before the weekend ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"the State Department has now flagged 22 of her emails as top secret","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"-- so sensitive , in fact ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"that they can not be released , even in redacted form :","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"Fox News has also reported","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"that some 'beyond top secret ' information is also being withheld entirely .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"The `` innocuous `` damage control fairy tale is dead ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"killed off by the Inspector General and the Obama State Department .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Team Clinton 's preposterous `` Republicans and their allies `` conspiracy theory suffers yet another body blow :","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"Intelligence community sources confirm","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that this intelligence was top secret and above from the very moment","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"it hit her vulnerable server ;","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"it was not upgraded retroactively .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"And then there 's this crucial detail","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"That would be the same Sidney Blumenthal","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"who 'd been barred from official service by the Obama White House","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"because of his unethical reputation ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"the same Sidney Blumenthal","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"whose email correspondence","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Hillary has claimed","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"was strictly personal and not at all work-related ,","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"and the same Sidney Blumenthal","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"whom","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Hillary swore under oath","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"was not an adviser of hers , `` official or unofficial . ''","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"Lie upon lie .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"This man was trafficking in extremely secret US intelligence","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"while working as an off-the-books advisor to Mrs. Clinton , in direct violation of Obama 's wishes","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"( while being paid by the Clinton Foundation ) ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"and his emails unquestionably related to her work as Secretary of State .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"That 's even clearer","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"now that the Obama administration has decided to withhold an entire email of his due to its top secret contents ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"calling it too dangerous to release .","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"Keep in mind","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"that he did not have access to secure government email systems","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"through which to send such intelligence ,","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"as required ,","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"because he was explicitly banned from government service .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"He was sending this stuff from his unsecure account to Hillary 's unsecure account .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"And yes , his unsecure account was hacked","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"-- which is how we found out about the work-related emails","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"Hillary withheld","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"and destroyed in the first place .","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"This series of disastrous revelations prompted panicky Democrats to kick their partisan spin into hyperdrive .","depth":5},{"id":125,"text":"Hillary 's spokesman blamed the situation on `` over-classification run amok , ''","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"pretending","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"as though the top secret and SAP intel","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"his boss compromised","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"should n't have been classified at all .","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"Out of curiosity ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"even if this ridiculous argument were true ,","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"how on earth would he know ?","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"Has he personally seen this 'need to know ' intelligence ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"which requires top-level security clearance ?","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"And","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"while we 're looking through the `` how would they know ? '' file ,","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"check this out","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"The White House is simultaneously insisting","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"that there 's been no political influence in this case whatsoever ,","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"yet Obama 's press secretary is telling reporters","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"that they do n't expect an indictment ...","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"a decision-making process","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"that is supposedly the sole purview of the allegedly non-political Justice Department .","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"Something smells rotten already ;","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"this marks the second instance of apparent White House interference .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"One hopes","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"FBI Director James Comey is paying attention .","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"For what it 's worth ,","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"the crew at MSNBC 's Morning Joe has been hearing the opposite from their sources .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"( Quote :","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"`` All of our sources high up are telling us ...","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"that this investigation is far more advanced","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"than we the public knows '' ) .","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"Meanwhile , the top Democrat on the Senate Intelligence Committee","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"-- who has been known to indulge in shameful hackery","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"when the politics call for it --","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"has put out a `` nothing to see here ``","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"statement","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"that avoids a slew of inconvenient details :","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"This is utter garbage .","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"The `` marked classified '' excuse is totally bunk ,","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"as acknowledged by Hillary Clinton herself .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"She signed a binding nondisclosure form upon assuming office","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"that specifically stated","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"that she was required to recognize and protect all classified material , `` marked or unmarked . ''","depth":13},{"id":166,"text":"These secret emails were born classified at the very highest levels .","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"Her handling of them appears to have been flagrantly reckless and negligent ,","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"which is a federal crime .","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"All the verbiage about the emails `` originating '' from someone other than Hillary is also irrelevant nonsense .","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"The reason","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"this problem exists","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"is that she exclusively used an unsecure , private server","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"to conduct all of her official business .","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"This violated `` clear-cut `` rules ,","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"according to data security experts and a Clinton-appointed federal judge .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"In 2011 , she was personally and explicitly warned by State Department security officials","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"that foreign hackers were seeking to infiltrate US officials ' systems","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"by targeting their private emails .","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"She chose to carry on with her appallingly under-secured scheme anyway .","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"This entire scandal `` originated '' with Hillary","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"because she 's the one","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"who ordered the server set up and activated in the first place .","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"She 's the one","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"who used it year after year ,","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"knowingly putting national security at risk .","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"And she 's the one","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"who 's lied about it at every turn .","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"Her story has morphed from'there was no classified material on the server '","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"( false , roughly 1,600 times over ) ,","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"to ' I did n't send or receive anything","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"that was classified '","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"( false ) ,","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"to'nothing was classified at the time '","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"( false ) ,","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"to'nothing was marked classified '","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"( irrelevant , and still possibly false ,","depth":15},{"id":197,"text":"depending on what she deleted ) ,","depth":15},{"id":198,"text":"to'that top secret and beyond material did n't originate from me . '","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"And even that is n't true","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"I 'll leave you with a few facts , and an assessment from a former NSA official","depth":11},{"id":201,"text":"who 's intimately familiar with classification laws and protocols :","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"The seriousness of the classified material","depth":13},{"id":203,"text":"confirmed to be on her private server","depth":13},{"id":204,"text":"is escalating .","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"The final","depth":13},{"id":206,"text":"( ludicrously delayed )","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"email dump ought to be a real doozie .","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"And again , these court-ordered disclosures only entail the messages","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"she and her lawyers did n't unilaterally delete","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"without any oversight ,","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"and about which she 's lied .","depth":10},{"id":212,"text":"The Federal Bureau of Investigation is all over it .","depth":8},{"id":213,"text":"This is far from over .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":427,"left":0,"right":426,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":426,"left":282,"right":425,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":219,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":216,"right":218,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":215,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":215,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":218,"left":217,"righ